dct_title_s: Islas Canarias / Mapa editado por la Sección Cartográfica de Firestone Hispania, S.A. (Recto)
dct_description_sm: "4-0170." Relief shown by shading, and spot heights. Legend in Spanish, French, and English. Some sites are shown pictorially. Includes location map and tables of "Datos climatológicos" and "Equivalencias útiles para turistas." Includes on verso: Index, tourist information, street nomenclature.
